name: I don't know what I'm doing and I love it
description:
Piece #6 of the collection:
I'm not your therapist but I'd like to cheer you up with my dorky art

The series focuses on the fragility of the inner world and brings up topics that we often find in our long journey on earth. 

#6
When I'm creating, I don't know what I am doing, and I love it.
Try yourself, do something without knowing why. You will love it.
